### SSH MULTIPLEXING ###
ControlMaster auto
ControlPath ~/.ssh/sockets/socket-%r@%h:%p
ControlPersist 120
### SSH MULTIPLEXING ###

### SSH CLIPBOARD FORWARDING ###
# Forward OSC 52 escape sequences for clipboard forwarding over SSH
# This allows tmux copy mode to forward clipboard to local machine
SetEnv LC_TERMINAL=1
### SSH CLIPBOARD FORWARDING ###
